{"tid":516503,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)新年節目","createTime":"2018-01-01T13:05:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T20:35:51.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e279f042c28401784d49a3e0515f49bac293b107","tid":516503,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T13:05:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=bThROXMWT9S%2Fy0S8rVjPEDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=7f6653f8\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=bThROXMWT9S%2Fy0S8rVjPEDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=e9591e61\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/4/46/Life_2017_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F4%2F46%2FLife_2017_Poster.jpg&h=21cc14fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/6/6f/Ouija_Origin_of_Evil_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F6%2F6f%2FOuija_Origin_of_Evil_Poster.jpg&h=4e431917&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/1/11/V_for_Vendetta.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F1%2F11%2FV_for_Vendetta.jpg&h=3b449eb1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/bc/Interstellar_film_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fbc%2FInterstellar_film_poster.jpg&h=542b3efb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事敘述六名國際太空站的成員的任務是研究火星上的某種樣本，這樣本很可能是第一個外星生命的證明，但也發現此生命的智能比想像中的高..<br />\n<br />\n2.故事設定於前集的五十年前，位在1967年的洛杉磯，敘述一名寡婦艾莉絲&middot;詹德因已故家人的緣故而會使用假的降神會，以來欺騙客人。然而，當家人發現了一個占卜盤後，使得詹德家最小的女兒朵莉絲被邪惡的惡靈糾纏，使得母女三人為了拯救朵莉絲而想辦法應付其恐怖遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n3.天主教徒蓋&middot;福克斯因試圖炸毀上議院以推翻逼害天主教的英國政府而被捕，並在隨後被絞殺。接著電影閃到四百多年後的2020年，此時的英國由一個受法西斯政黨「北方之火」控制的極權政府統治。艾薇&middot;哈蒙德是一名年輕的勞工階級女子，在一次違反宵禁外出時遭一群「Fingermen」成員圍堵，當他們正欲圖謀不軌之時，一名戴著蓋&middot;福克斯面具的男子將艾薇從他們的手中救了出來。他將他的名字「V」告訴了艾薇..<br />\n<br />\n4.地球農作物因氣候轉變及枯萎病而經常失收，曾是美國國家航空暨太空總署的工程師和火箭駕駛員的主角庫珀（Cooper）被迫成為農民以協助解決糧食危機。庫珀的10歲女兒墨菲（Murphy）發現其房間書架上的書本無故掉到地上，認為這是騷靈現象。不久後，一場沙塵暴在墨菲房間中留下了坐標通訊碼，二人驅車到達坐標位置後發現那是北美空防司令部（已成為美國國家航空暨太空總署的秘密基地）<br />\n<br />\n10 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=bThROXMWT9S%2Fy0S8rVjPEDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=9ab71ef4\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=bThROXMWT9S%2Fy0S8rVjPEDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=2c8e6449\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2165b0a20aef194f27a731a2a77475e6848d0bf5","tid":516503,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T13:12:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20158dd4025304922123eef892243caafad716b1","tid":516503,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T13:44:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4fc428d2bd46302b54f726bdb63f4733e603314","tid":516503,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T15:10:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0682466b97d2d10e1c91ccb539444bf924ebf5b","tid":516503,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T15:48:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c4fbfd6cd3f09304779e31ca5a099f2bb5f758","tid":516503,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T16:56:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"330a03fbb7987cc63f8196989a53174d257b8e54","tid":516503,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:27:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad7515724ea3b05f5d0f4b6b71349733d7abc17","tid":516503,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:49:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef96d289e774119a8f6b159a672004eb2eca834","tid":516503,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T19:03:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/as